1
00:00:05,686 --> 00:00:09,615
Who can I tell? Who would believe me?

2
00:00:09,679 --> 00:00:12,471
[Visa for the Spiritual World]

3
00:00:12,825 --> 00:00:16,470
Only faith.

4
00:00:17,043 --> 00:00:19,505
It’s very interesting, Kṛṣṇa consciousness;

5
00:00:19,505 --> 00:00:22,559
you cannot capture it with your intellect.

6
00:00:22,667 --> 00:00:24,971
Jñāne prayāsam udapāsya
namanta eva (SB: 10.14.3).

7
00:00:24,971 --> 00:00:26,353
Can’t get it.

8
00:00:26,353 --> 00:00:30,233
Two fingers too short; ‘dve angala’.

9
00:00:30,480 --> 00:00:33,025
You’ll always be two fingers too short.

10
00:00:33,025 --> 00:00:37,458
There’ll always be a little
“just can't understand this one part”;

11
00:00:37,458 --> 00:00:39,691
“won’t connect.”

12
00:00:40,025 --> 00:00:42,713
That’s the intellect falling short;

13
00:00:42,713 --> 00:00:47,793
the bee trying to taste the honey

14
00:00:47,793 --> 00:00:52,218
but doesn’t see that it’s the glass barrier,

15
00:00:53,074 --> 00:00:57,976
the glass barrier of curiosity; intellect;

16
00:00:58,115 --> 00:00:59,991
the need to know.

17
00:00:59,991 --> 00:01:02,712
Guru Mahārāj said, just as karma

18
00:01:02,712 --> 00:01:04,949
−it's clear, karma has to be given up−

19
00:01:04,949 --> 00:01:07,406
he’s saying curiosity has to be given up too;

20
00:01:07,406 --> 00:01:10,704
jñān, the desire to know.

21
00:01:13,983 --> 00:01:17,469
Anyone who wants to know,
who’s too suspicious,

22
00:01:17,469 --> 00:01:19,483
that’s not good.

23
00:01:25,933 --> 00:01:30,173
You want to immigrate to some country,

24
00:01:30,361 --> 00:01:34,902
say someone wanted to immigrate to Russia …

25
00:01:36,662 --> 00:01:38,970
You laugh.

26
00:01:39,907 --> 00:01:41,992
Once I was giving a lecture in Kiev,

27
00:01:41,992 --> 00:01:45,188
it was on the fifteen-hundredth
anniversary of Kiev,

28
00:01:45,234 --> 00:01:48,253
and there was this government agent at the lecture,

29
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:51,289
and then he wanted to see my passport.

30
00:01:51,289 --> 00:01:53,746
And then all the people were saying,

31
00:01:53,746 --> 00:01:57,481
"What are you …?" You know,
they were chastising him.

32
00:01:57,496 --> 00:01:59,388
And then he was trying to give an excuse

33
00:01:59,388 --> 00:02:00,736
for why he was doing this, he said,

34
00:02:00,767 --> 00:02:02,589
“Well, you know,
there’s so many people trying

35
00:02:02,589 --> 00:02:05,722
to enter this country illegally.”

36
00:02:06,265 --> 00:02:11,415
And everyone said,
“So an American is trying to

37
00:02:11,612 --> 00:02:15,360
enter the Ukraine illegally?”
[Laughs]

38
00:02:21,947 --> 00:02:26,549
But if you did want to become
a Russian citizen,

39
00:02:26,549 --> 00:02:28,261
and from the very beginning, you say,

40
00:02:28,261 --> 00:02:35,317
"I'm very fascinated by the
FSB, the KGB.”

41
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:41,239
They'll say, “You’re just a beginner,

42
00:02:41,239 --> 00:02:43,284
why do you want to know those things?

43
00:02:43,284 --> 00:02:46,617
Why do you want to know
confidential secret things?

44
00:02:46,617 --> 00:02:51,763
And you know, you haven’t even
filled out an application.”

45
00:02:52,434 --> 00:02:54,939
So Guru Mahārāj said,
“Passport is not enough;

46
00:02:54,939 --> 00:02:56,892
you need a visa.”

47
00:02:57,091 --> 00:03:02,689
But you don’t even have a visa proper
for entry into the spiritual world,

48
00:03:02,689 --> 00:03:11,926
but need to know all the intricate secrets
of Kṛṣṇa conception.

49
00:03:13,415 --> 00:03:17,039
Guru Mahārāj said that in this world,
men and women

50
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:22,068
are more discreet about their activities,

51
00:03:22,608 --> 00:03:29,036
and you want to know about this,
that and the other thing, about divinity?

52
00:03:29,036 --> 00:03:34,566
That's not going to be looked upon
favourably in your visa application.

53
00:03:36,236 --> 00:03:41,306
You’re granted a visa when it’s been determined

54
00:03:41,306 --> 00:03:45,647
by the country you’re seeking admission to

55
00:03:45,647 --> 00:03:49,683
that it’s in their interest to bring you in.

56
00:03:49,683 --> 00:03:52,661
We already know you have some interest.

57
00:03:52,661 --> 00:03:56,321
“Oh, I already have, I’m chanting Hare Kṛṣṇa.”

58
00:03:57,843 --> 00:04:00,018
Good for you.

59
00:04:03,751 --> 00:04:07,289
But it has to be in their interest to bring you in,

60
00:04:07,289 --> 00:04:08,941
they’re looking for servitors,

61
00:04:08,941 --> 00:04:12,568
they’re not looking for bead counters.

62
00:04:14,322 --> 00:04:20,272
Guru Mahārāj said, “You don't see pictures
of Vraja-gopīs chanting on japa-mālā,

63
00:04:20,777 --> 00:04:25,892
but you see pictures of them churning butter."

